{
  "stem": "18486.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Do you know where they are?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, things like that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Or have you ever been affiliated with any work for Jewish people, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[DRINKS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We have had narrow escapes, yeah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Very narrow.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, for instance, once they came, and we were absolutely not aware of it that they were coming.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Usually-- you see, we lived a little bit on the outside of a village-- Laren was a village-- and there was one policeman who was in our group.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody else knew that, of course, than our group members.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he had-- had taken care of the fact that we had a telephone-- we were-- that our telephone was connected.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because we lived on a dead end road which ended-- ended in very large nature reservation, with [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he played up very much to the German commander, the danger of a fire in the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because the Germans would also have maneuvers there in the-- in the-- in that place.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so they said, we need somebody who lives there, who we can trust, and who must have a telephone to warn when there is a fire.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And under that pretext, we had a telephone.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Of course, it didn't help us much, because no-- none of our friends or anybody else had a telephone.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But it helped us only, very much, with this policeman.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because when the Germans came to our village, where we lived a little bit outside, he would give us a call.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That means he would ring twice and hang up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Then we knew there was danger.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Then all of the Jewish people could hide.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that helped us tremendously, of course.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had several, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That one time-- that was the worst time.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
